description.en: COCOIN is a new community-driven deflationary crypto currency with an anti whale and anti pump & dump policy. Devs doxxed, founded in The Netherlands & 100% transparant. $COCO is here to stay. Here to change the game. $COCO is for those who want to create a better life than their parents could. For those who are looking to win. 2% of each sell order goes to charity as we believe giving is what makes us real winners.
